#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:1
msgid "HTTP API"
msgstr "HTTP API"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:3
msgid "HTTP client helpers are available under `ptool.http` and `p.http`."
msgstr "HTTP 客户端辅助能力位于 `ptool.http` 和 `p.http` 下。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:5
msgid "ptool.http.request"
msgstr "ptool.http.request"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:7
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:7"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:9
msgid ""
"`ptool.http.request(options)` sends an HTTP request and returns a `Response` "
"object."
msgstr "`ptool.http.request(options)` 发送一个 HTTP 请求，并返回 `Response` 对象。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:12
msgid "`options` fields:"
msgstr "`options` 字段："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:14
msgid "`url` (string, required): The request URL."
msgstr "`url`（string，必填）：请求 URL。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:15
msgid "`method` (string, optional): The HTTP method. Defaults to `\"GET\"`."
msgstr "`method`（string，可选）：HTTP 方法。默认值为 `\"GET\"`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:16
msgid ""
"`headers` (table, optional): Request headers, where both keys and values are "
"strings."
msgstr "`headers`（table，可选）：请求头，键和值都必须是字符串。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:18
msgid ""
"`query` (table, optional): Query parameters appended to the request URL. "
"Keys must be strings. Values may be strings, numbers, or booleans."
msgstr "`query`（table，可选）：追加到请求 URL 的查询参数。键必须是字符串，值可以 是"
"字符串、数字或布尔值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:20
msgid "`body` (string, optional): The request body."
msgstr "`body`（string，可选）：请求体。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:21
msgid ""
"`json` (Lua value, optional): A Lua value encoded as JSON and used as the "
"request body. When `content-type` is not already set, it defaults to `"
"application/json`."
msgstr ""
"`json`（Lua 值，可选）：会被编码为 JSON 并作为请求体发送。当未显式设置 "
"`content-type` 时，默认使用 `application/json`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:24
msgid ""
"`form` (table, optional): Form fields encoded as `application/x-www-form-"
"urlencoded` and used as the request body. Keys must be strings. Values may "
"be strings, numbers, or booleans."
msgstr ""
"`form`（table，可选）：会被编码为 `application/x-www-form-urlencoded` 并作为"
"请求体发送。键必须是字符串，值 可以是字符串、数字或布尔值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:27
msgid ""
"`timeout_ms` (integer, optional): Timeout in milliseconds. Defaults to "
"`30000`."
msgstr "`timeout_ms`（integer，可选）：超时时间，单位毫秒。默认值为 `30000`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:29
msgid ""
"`connect_timeout_ms` (integer, optional): Connection timeout in milliseconds."
msgstr "`connect_timeout_ms`（integer，可选）：连接超时时间，单位毫秒。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:30
msgid ""
"`follow_redirects` (boolean, optional): Whether redirects should be followed."
msgstr "`follow_redirects`（boolean，可选）：是否跟随重定向。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:31
msgid ""
"`max_redirects` (integer, optional): Maximum number of redirects to follow."
msgstr "`max_redirects`（integer，可选）：允许跟随的最大重定向次数。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:32
msgid "`user_agent` (string, optional): Sets the `user-agent` request header."
msgstr "`user_agent`（string，可选）：设置 `user-agent` 请求头。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:33
msgid ""
"`basic_auth` (table, optional): HTTP basic auth credentials with string "
"fields `username` and `password`."
msgstr "`basic_auth`（table，可选）：HTTP Basic 认证信息，包含字符串字段 `username` "
"和 `password`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:35
msgid ""
"`bearer_token` (string, optional): Bearer token used for the `authorization` "
"header."
msgstr "`bearer_token`（string，可选）：用于 `authorization` 请求头的 Bearer Token。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:37
msgid ""
"`fail_on_http_error` (boolean, optional): When `true`, raise an error for "
"4xx and 5xx HTTP responses. Defaults to `false`."
msgstr ""
"`fail_on_http_error`（boolean，可选）：为 `true` 时，4xx 和 5xx HTTP 响应会直"
"接抛错。默认值为 `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:40
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:40"
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:42
msgid "`body`, `json`, and `form` are mutually exclusive."
msgstr "`body`、`json` 和 `form` 互斥。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:43
msgid "`basic_auth` and `bearer_token` are mutually exclusive."
msgstr "`basic_auth` 和 `bearer_token` 互斥。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:45
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:69
msgid "Response"
msgstr "Response"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:71
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:71"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:73
msgid ""
"`Response` represents an HTTP response returned by `ptool.http.request(...)`."
msgstr "`Response` 表示 `ptool.http.request(...)` 返回的 HTTP 响应。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:75
msgid "Fields:"
msgstr "字段："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:77
msgid "`status` (integer): The HTTP status code."
msgstr "`status`（integer）：HTTP 状态码。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:78
msgid "`ok` (boolean): Whether the status code is in the 2xx range."
msgstr "`ok`（boolean）：状态码是否位于 2xx 范围内。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:79
msgid "`url` (string): The final URL after redirects."
msgstr "`url`（string）：重定向后的最终 URL。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:80
msgid ""
"`headers` (table): A flattened convenience view of response headers "
"(`table<string, string>`). Repeated headers are merged with `, `."
msgstr ""
"`headers`（table）：响应头的扁平化便捷视图（`table<string, string>`）。 重复"
"响应头会使用 `, ` 合并。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:83
msgid "Methods:"
msgstr "方法："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:85
msgid "`resp:text()`: Reads and returns the response body as text."
msgstr "`resp:text()`：读取并以文本形式返回响应体。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:86
msgid ""
"`resp:json()`: Reads the response body, parses it as JSON, and returns a Lua "
"value."
msgstr "`resp:json()`：读取响应体，按 JSON 解析后返回 Lua 值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:88
msgid "`resp:bytes()`: Reads and returns the raw bytes (as a Lua string)."
msgstr "`resp:bytes()`：读取并返回原始字节（作为 Lua 字符串）。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:89
msgid ""
"`resp:header(name)`: Returns the first matching response header value, or "
"`nil`."
msgstr "`resp:header(name)`：返回第一个匹配的响应头值，若不存在则返回 `nil`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:91
msgid ""
"`resp:header_values(name)`: Returns all matching response header values as "
"an array."
msgstr "`resp:header_values(name)`：返回所有匹配的响应头值数组。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:93
msgid ""
"`resp:raise_for_status()`: Raises an error for 4xx and 5xx HTTP responses."
msgstr "`resp:raise_for_status()`：对 4xx 和 5xx HTTP 响应抛出错误。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:95
msgid "text"
msgstr "text"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:97
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:text`."
msgstr "规范 API 名称：`ptool.http.Response:text`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:99
msgid "`resp:text()` reads and returns the response body as text."
msgstr "`resp:text()` 读取并以文本形式返回响应体。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:101
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:101"
msgid "Returns: `string`."
msgstr "返回：`string`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:103
msgid "json"
msgstr "json"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:105
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:json`."
msgstr "规范 API 名称：`ptool.http.Response:json`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:107
msgid ""
"`resp:json()` reads the response body, parses it as JSON, and returns a Lua "
"value."
msgstr "`resp:json()` 读取响应体，按 JSON 解析后返回 Lua 值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:110
msgid "bytes"
msgstr "bytes"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:112
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:bytes`."
msgstr "规范 API 名称：`ptool.http.Response:bytes`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:114
msgid "`resp:bytes()` reads and returns the response body as raw bytes."
msgstr "`resp:bytes()` 读取并以原始字节形式返回响应体。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:116
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:116"
msgid "Returns: `string`."
msgstr "返回：`string`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:118
msgid "header"
msgstr "header"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:120
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:header`."
msgstr "规范 API 名称：`ptool.http.Response:header`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:122
msgid ""
"`resp:header(name)` returns the first response header value matching `name`."
msgstr "`resp:header(name)` 返回第一个匹配 `name` 的响应头值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:124
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:124"
msgid "`name` (string, required): The header name to look up."
msgstr "`name`（string，必填）：要查找的响应头名称。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:125
msgid "Returns: `string | nil`."
msgstr "返回：`string | nil`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:127
msgid "header_values"
msgstr "header_values"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:129
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:header_values`."
msgstr "规范 API 名称：`ptool.http.Response:header_values`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:131
msgid ""
"`resp:header_values(name)` returns all response header values matching "
"`name`."
msgstr "`resp:header_values(name)` 返回所有匹配 `name` 的响应头值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:133
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:133"
msgid "`name` (string, required): The header name to look up."
msgstr "`name`（string，必填）：要查找的响应头名称。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:134
msgid "Returns: `string[]`."
msgstr "返回：`string[]`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:136
msgid "raise_for_status"
msgstr "raise_for_status"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:138
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.http.Response:raise_for_status`."
msgstr "规范 API 名称：`ptool.http.Response:raise_for_status`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:140
msgid ""
"`resp:raise_for_status()` raises an error when the response status code is "
"in the 4xx or 5xx range."
msgstr "`resp:raise_for_status()` 会在响应状态码处于 4xx 或 5xx 范围时抛出错误。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:143
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:143"
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:145
msgid ""
"Non-2xx HTTP statuses do not raise errors by default. Callers can check "
"`resp.ok`, set `fail_on_http_error = true`, or call "
"`resp:raise_for_status()`."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，非 2xx HTTP 状态不会抛错。调用方可以检查 `resp.ok`、设置 `"
"fail_on_http_error = true`，或调用 `resp:raise_for_status()`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/http.md:147
msgid ""
"The response body is cached after the first read. Calling `text`, `json`, "
"and `bytes` multiple times is allowed."
msgstr "响应体会在首次读取后缓存，因此 `text`、`json` 和 `bytes` 可以重复调用。"
